de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class CheckList

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.CheckList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IInfo, Serializable, Comparable<CheckList>

    public class CheckList
extends Object
implements Comparable<CheckList>, IInfo, Serializable
    The check list for the operator. The operator can insert completed processing steps into the list. It's used to save the actions of the previous operators and get the information which tasks are open.
    See Also:
